#  Smart Goal Planner

A React-based application that helps users plan, track, and manage their savings goals effectively. Users can set financial goals, track their progress with deposits, and get a visual overview of their savings journey.

##  Features

-  Add new savings goals (name, target amount, deadline)
-  Make deposits toward each goal
-  View progress as a percentage bar or chart
-  Delete goals and deposits
-  Backend powered by `json-server`

